---
title: Roasted Cauliflower & Pearl Couscous Salad with Goat Cheese & Flaked Almonds
description: We love the tender texture of pearl couscous, each grain holds its shape and it easily handles bold flavours. Combine that with spiced roasted veggies, creamy goat cheese and fresh salad leaves and this is a salad to remember!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bc52400ae08b552ce0fd402-5efabfe5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/roast-cauliflower-goat-cheese-salad-5bc52400ae08b552ce0fd402-bafda810.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/roasted-cauliflower-and-pearl-couscous-salad-5bc52400ae08b552ce0fd402
